{"tid":1485830,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[記憶麵包] 請謹記香港人到呢一刻仲係輸緊俾中國共產黨","createTime":"2019-08-18T16:50:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T03:17:42.000Z","uid":161684,"like":136,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"c63e6f00726220faa4487cf37c567a6b2ba7da3a","tid":1485830,"uid":161684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:50:35.000Z","msg":"係 呢排外國傳來唔少好消息<br />\n係 今日難得有好多人冒雨集會<br />\n但係 淋完雨返屋企一上連登 不安就湧埋黎<br />\n<br />\n1. 見到熱門上大部分嘅post都係指責緊人唔散水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OwaJXj4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOwaJXj4.png&h=1d907410&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 俾位人入嘅論調重新出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UprJcTq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUprJcTq.png&h=b87d05b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 話唔好衰收尾 唔好廢左武功 但明明未有重大成果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/crzbmMM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcrzbmMM.png&h=7dae253b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 用撚樣稱呼前線（你話佢地係鬼都冇咁嬲）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6k0xQE7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6k0xQE7.png&h=8f1ea2d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 我地個目標幾時變左「造就一個和理非」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pbh8oZ7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpbh8oZ7.png&h=588c1e48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6. 最撚癲嘅係全部以上留言都唔係P牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 我唔係勇武前線 可能冇咩資格講野<br />\n但我知道無論今日我淋到成身濕曬 今日個畫面幾感人<br />\n呢場仗我地仲係輸緊架 所有人都仲係逍遙法外呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然唔知下一步應該要做咩 <br />\n雖然判斷唔到點先算中計 邊班人係鬼係對家假扮<br />\n但係有一樣野係一定唔會錯嘅 就係<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">拒絕遺忘</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ymA4WzKtNE0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FymA4WzKtNE0&d=T%2BmtXVGNOTzTHFJD9Tq3ceBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=128bd486\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ymA4WzKtNE0</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WVcTCzE4nHM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWVcTCzE4nHM&d=T%2BmtXVGNOTzTHFJD9Tq3ceBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=9b488da7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WVcTCzE4nHM</a> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nfzQW1VpJW4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DnfzQW1VpJW4&d=T%2BmtXVGNOTzTHFJD9Tq3ceBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=7be7b8ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nfzQW1VpJW4</a> <br />\n<br />\n試下完整咁睇一次每條片 即使唔忍心睇都唔好停頓<br />\n因為人總係會一廂情願想一切照常 人總係好容易俾惰性支配<br />\n但係如果我地要從<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中國共產黨 特區政府 警察 黑社會</span></strong> 手上<br />\n奪回香港 我地嘅屋企<br />\n我地就要好記性 一於記佢老味！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"e7f48c0bfa739381c33fabb430bad7ae9eaa0b3c","tid":1485830,"uid":161684,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:53:44.000Z","msg":"Tui!"},{"pid":"1a3d361d61a492628842c8e1c8fb6f0fefccf3f3","tid":1485830,"uid":161684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:53:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fb2d757c357