日後日直到抗爭成功，都要幫手繼續出招啦，唔好以為行完就得。<br />\n<br />\n今日係表態，我地無贏過。<br />\n<br />\n今日充分表現和理非勇武不割蓆。<br />\n<br />\n賣港政府，黑警，共匪，藍絲，無時無刻想我地仆街死。<br />\n<br />\n千萬唔好自我感覺良好，求下大家。<br />\n<br />\n我地無退路，聯合外國勢力，絕地反擊。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可。<br />\n<br />\n香港警察，知法犯法。<br />\n<br />\n黑警，還眼。<br />\n<br />\n香港人，加油。<br />\n<br />\nFight for freedom, Stand with Hong Kong."},{"pid":"00f54f8fa62b5e9e08ffc2848a3a2a791b660d9e","tid":1485830,"uid":161684,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b85611e2a85fd4b9a545f14bc48e4f4c99eed0c4","tid":1485830,"uid":50779,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:54:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:00:25.000Z","msg":"曱甴生命力最撚頑強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"462cf3df75531b8f9281fb17df14da532eb9ea51","tid":1485830,"uid":161684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39c02a57afe3d523ac704df04588627fd25c6718","tid":1485830,"uid":235025,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:58:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:01:21.000Z","msg":"Exactly!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ca8a3d1b9cbd4748760c7e6dc9bd10fed2776cf","tid":1485830,"uid":200464,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:02:06.000Z","msg":"PUSH<br />\n唔明點解大家要一路屌，可能你地唔同意前線，<br />\n但係佢地都好辛苦架，體諒下啦好唔好，<br />\n我知道大家都緊張佢地，我都一樣係，<br />\n但係一定要俾啲信心佢地，<br />\n如果冇咗信任，我地仲可以點樣行落去。<br />\n今日大家都攰啦，早啲抖下，之後再慢慢諗下可以點樣做得更加好啦"},{"pid":"7cab1f61d8fd87660d8087a540e2329a041829c1","tid":1485830,"uid":161684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6831f1639ae83b1f8ab56b251bc139cee1f0ad5c","tid":1485830,"uid":16025,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:59:10.000Z","msg":"聽日後日直到抗爭成功，都要幫手繼續出招啦，唔好以為行完就得。<br />\n<br />\n今日係表態，我地無贏過。<br />\n<br />\n今日充分表現和理非勇武不割蓆。<br />\n<br />\n賣港政府，黑警，共匪，藍絲，無時無刻想我地仆街死。<br />\n<br />\n千萬唔好自我感覺良好，求下大家。<br />\n<br />\n我地無退路，聯合外國勢力，絕地反擊。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可。<br />\n<br />\n香港警察，知法犯法。<br />\n<br />\n黑警，還眼。<br />\n<br />\n香港人，加油。<br />\n<br />\nFight for freedom, Stand with Hong Kong."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:03:22.000Z","msg":"開心一陣好喇<br />\n認清敵人<br />\n認清形勢<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">屌那媽 頂硬上</span></span>"},{"pid":"dd0a60722c6c8c520126fce668491518f74f3d3d","tid":1485830,"uid":14091,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:04:29.000Z","msg":"我都有份叫人走<br />\n但我無唔記得咁多個義士同手足<br />\n我係覺得<span style=\"color: red;\">今日</span>目標真係和理非<br />\n所以先咁多人同我一樣想用唔同既論調叫人走<br />\n\b依加170萬人走出黎都咁和平<br />\n已經係一把好強既武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然唔可以浸淫係今晚既和理非成功<br />\n五大訴求都無覆過<br />\n大家繼續努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96aa6a3ebb53ba99fbdbc9a4684dc38cb8573423","tid":1485830,"uid":161684,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1ca8a3d1b9cbd4748760c7e6dc9bd10fed2776cf","tid":1485830,"uid":200464,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:02:06.000Z","msg":"PUSH<br />\n唔明點解大家要一路屌，可能你地唔同意前線，<br />\n但係佢地都好辛苦架，體諒下啦好唔好，<br />\n我知道大家都緊張佢地，我都一樣係，<br />\n但係一定要俾啲信心佢地，<br />\n如果冇咗信任，我地仲可以點樣行落去。<br />\n今日大家都攰啦，早啲抖下，之後再慢慢諗下可以點樣做得更加好啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:11:24.000Z","msg":"先莫論前線對錯 <br />\n討論重點根本就唔應該放係呢d位上<br />\n留同唔留係咪有咁大影響呢<br />\n就正如果日機場 連登上講到好大鑊咁<br />\n但外國媒體根本就冇focus係付國豪度<br />\n所以連登情勢真係幾不安下"},{"pid":"c903f5e772f4c2b19fa71b5861dcd2a62619d4b7","tid":1485830,"uid":161684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:12:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"324aed04d791c11d8a563c6ee225d968a703521e","tid":1485830,"uid":15696,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:13:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qANz4of.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqANz4of.png&h=0ec10d49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T1OGKog.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT1OGKog.png&h=4e41f387&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"80b1e8f0d5e71d270dde26ffc31c78e5fe422685","tid":1485830,"uid":36089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:13:32.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，借一借位～<br />\n<br />\n<strong>解放軍係10分鐘之內就可以落黎香港<br />\n美國可以一夜之間取消香港關係法<br />\n隨便一樣野都足以致命<br />\n令所有外資撤退，港元急速貶值</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>保護自己資產，全民唱美元現鈔！</strong></span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1478882\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1478882</a>"},{"pid":"d789d7cdb0f674f450dbfebc0cd5e6cc54ead2fd","tid":1485830,"uid":2377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00f54f8fa62b5e9e08ffc2848a3a2a791b660d9e","tid":1485830,"uid":161684,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b85611e2a85fd4b9a545f14bc48e4f4c99eed0c4","tid":1485830,"uid":50779,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:54:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:00:25.000Z","msg":"曱甴生命力最撚頑強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:14:31.000Z","msg":"屌你老母自乏做乜撚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9616fd6c5a223dd7b6cb0c7c16f1a3eb22ba351b","tid":1485830,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:14:56.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"8d05d5a1981dd9f3577207ba3d476beb78a02b25","tid":1485830,"uid":2377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:15:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n7vYMuT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn7vYMuT.jpg&h=a06ab505&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>曱甴生命力最撚頑強<img src=\"/