994ea0b5d6b","tid":1485830,"uid":158524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:20:30.000Z","msg":"阻一阻你<br />\n<br />\n首先 好多謝你地 放棄自己寶貴嘅一日出嚟淋雨 <br />\n我地制造左一次又一次嘅記錄<br />\n但請 唔好因此而太過開心<br />\n我地五大訴求 一個都未達到<br />\n<br />\n再者 唔好再互相屌嚟屌去 互相捉鬼 好唔好？<br />\n唔想再變成雨革2.0嘅<br />\n請記得 不分化 不割席<br />\n我明白 有時候 大家每次都想出全力 <br />\n但喺 欲速則不達<br />\n<br />\n仲有我想求大家 繼續改變身邊同自己唔同意見嘅人<br />\n政治 唔係要一個人去認同你<br />\n政治 喺要令身邊意見分歧嘅人 思想上有改變而認同你<br />\n<br />\n最後我地點都好 唔好唔記得黑警做過乜 永遠都要追究佢地班仆街 <br />\n仲有香港人應承我 要永遠記得 嗰6位烈士"},{"pid":"90b1086573c1278ecb6e578600ac0d7ad1d5fc43","tid":1485830,"uid":161684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d3f2509fce1b9084cbec91742ba14d54fd8363d","tid":1485830,"uid":161684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:19:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iHcMa9r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiHcMa9r.png&h=fdf4eb53&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cXq2tV8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcXq2tV8.png&h=ec3d98b8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SoqU4uu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSoqU4uu.png&h=d350da3a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ef8fOWa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fef8fOWa.png&h=41cc9437&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/30HkfBb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F30HkfBb.png&h=03241884&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:20:46.000Z","msg":"Source: Maryjane W Tiffany"},{"pid":"b6eacaae1817530b4a84022d501b38e8f82e7e12","tid":1485830,"uid":279401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:20:46.000Z","msg":"中共不停報導香港反送中隨時會變成自爆!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1473197\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1473197</a>"},{"pid":"d0f22a5a4d0f0190bbc24c2c9f03b85aaffd47e2",