E8%90%BD%E6%A1%88%E8%B5%B7%E8%A8%B4%2F&d=T%2BmtXVGNOTzTHFJD9Tq3ceBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=aa258b60\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F721-%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E8%A5%B2%E6%93%8A-%E8%AD%A6%E5%86%8D%E6%8B%98-3-%E4%BA%BA%E6%B6%89%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E9%9B%86%E7%B5%90-%E7%B4%AF%E8%A8%88-27-%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E5%85%A8%E9%83%A8%E6%9C%AA%E8%90%BD%E6%A1%88%E8%B5%B7%E8%A8%B4%2F&h=bef8cf5c\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/721-元朗襲擊-警再拘-3-人涉非法集結-累計-27-人被捕-全部未落案起訴/</a><br />\n<br />\n 7 月21日元朗港鐵站發生襲擊事件，警方昨日公布拘捕多3名本地男子，涉嫌非法集結，案件被捕總人數增至27人。<br />\n<br />\n警方指出，昨日（8 月 8 日）上午分別在打鼓嶺分區及落馬洲分區再拘捕兩名分別 33 歲及 60 歲本地男子，以及於下午在天水圍分區拘捕一名 44 歲本地男子涉嫌非法集結，他們現正被扣留調查。<br />\n<br />\n721 元朗襲擊事件，被捕總人數增至27人，全部未落案起訴。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">恐佈組織中聯辦上個月對香港人發動襲擊<br />\n你同我講 佢係唔撚洗付出代價？<br />\n連推個人出黎代罪都唔撚洗？</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"239bb37ce0f7b74632e99766a8269570ca5d19f4","tid":1485830,"uid":161684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:53:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Dv0wWdoxeS8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDv0wWdoxeS8&d=T%2BmtXVGNOTzTHFJD9Tq3ceBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=5159922f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Dv0wWdoxeS8</a>"},{"pid":"e93b470a3bdc25024aa4413e346a377d9c6598f6","tid":1485830,"uid":161684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:55:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sjWWNiUKeX8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsjWWNiUKeX8&d=T%2BmtXVGNOTzTHFJD9Tq3ceBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=1fd769f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sjWWNiUKeX8</a>"},{"pid":"6c99d603b1247278c7c66b27